casebody.data:
Levon DEAN, Jr., petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 15-9260. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 28, 2016.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit granted limited to Question 2 presented by the petition.
